# Module 1: Introduction to Ethical Hacking
## Video content:
-> CIA: CIA stads for Confidentiality, Integrity and Availability. 
=> Cofidentiality is the piller that information is not accessed by unauthorized individuals. It involves using measures like Data encryption, Access control and strong authentication to protect personal and proprietary information. \
=> Integrity is the piller which focuses on maintaining the accuracy and consistency of data throughout its lifecyc;e. It guards against improper modification or destruction of information and ensures authenticity.
=> Availability is the piller ensures that systems and information are accessible and reliable for authorized users when they need them. It involves having systems and backups in place to handle high traffic and prevent downtime. \
